00:43:34.323 --> 00:43:37.659
Hey. Hey. wake up.

406
00:43:38.368 --> 00:43:41.413
We gotta go. Come on. wake up.
Come on. wake up.

407
00:43:41.496 --> 00:43:43.498
Wake up. Hey. Wake up!

